Append the following line to your .emacs file:

  (autoload 'rst-mode "rst-mode"
            "mode for editing reStructuredText documents" t)
  (setq auto-mode-alist
        (append '(("\\.rst$" . rst-mode)
                  ("\\.rest$" . rst-mode)) auto-mode-alist))

===========================================================================
